{"tid":1437151,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係機場播種玩冧中國政權","createTime":"2019-08-09T12:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T01:10:59.000Z","uid":258190,"like":36,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"816e8ddc02c4c1234603afb564b0ffaffe442a41","tid":1437151,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"機場太少中文資訊太多英文資訊<br />\n眼見好多華人由其是大陸人係睇唔明<br />\n如果我地想擁有更多支持者應該比多d中文資訊<br />\n洗佢地腦<br />\n坐得飛機黎香港人既大陸人都唔會太窮<br />\n改變思想應該由中產做起<br />\n因為佢地比較有學識比較容易去改做<br />\n依幾日要瘋狂洗佢地腦"},{"pid":"d12d04950baad30e4436ec2600f027924928ab6a","tid":1437151,"uid":152241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:47:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"91625eab7748138df5e8603edb69614a341eaf3c","tid":1437151,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0df4164dbda4677610fea094ac21c095c8f7d805","tid":1437151,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:54:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"004171eb8712e096fa1969ace3fd49ab728ff5aa","tid":1437151,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T12:59:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e221a4485ec2dc4baaff71aa3d8a892ff52f1b5b","tid":1437151,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:08:39.000Z","msg":"推呀推"},{"pid":"b406208093e7f77668f4593c108ca37fab34c816","tid":1437151,"uid":258190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:08:51.000Z","msg":"推爆佢得唔得"},{"pid":"1893d3e24756e8c71bbf97037ae5e92ef9ea6540","tid":1437151,"uid":118520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:09:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72110845e44c651ee978ab954a57f4189e552234","tid":1437151,"uid":160564,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T13:11: